trans-unit.source: Represents the <see cref="N:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures" /> or <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.StoryFragments" /> element of an <see cref="T:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument" />.
trans-unit.target: 表示 <see cref="N:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures" /> 的 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.StoryFragments" /> 或 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument" /> 項目。

trans-unit.source: This class has no public constructor.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別具有公用建構函式。

trans-unit.source: References to an <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsStructure> are obtained through the <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.IDocumentStructureProvider.AddDocumentStructure%2A> or <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.IStoryFragmentProvider.AddStoryFragment%2A> methods.

For more information about the <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures> or <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.StoryFragments> elements of an <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument>, see Chapter 9 in the *XPS Paper Specification (XPS)* which you can download at [http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=65761](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=65761).
trans-unit.target: 如需有關<xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures>或<xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.StoryFragments>的項目<xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument>，請參閱第 9 章中*XPS 文件規格 (XPS)*您可以在下載[ http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=65761 ](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=65761).
